---
title: Caesar Chicken Burgers with Parmesan Potato Coins
description: Look out! Chicken Caesar salad is getting made-over into a burger! Savoury, Caesar-y dressing is delicious spread onto buttery, toasted burger buns and as a dipper for Parmesan potato coins!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-cesar-au-poulet-dc8f96dd.jpg
